The paper discusses network security, which is a subfield of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses cryptographic protocols, packet filtering, and dynamic resource allocation, which are all topics related to network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also discusses interactions between security mechanisms, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed computing (cs.DC). Finally, the paper discusses the role of networks in cyber-security, which is a topic related to social and information networks (cs.SI).
